《'''Lyrical Sympathy'''》是日本[[視覺系|視覺系]]搖滾樂團[[Versailles|Versailles]]於2007年10月31日發行的首張[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]，也是他們的出道作品。<ref>{{cite web
| title = ''Lyrical Sympathy'' details
| work = cdjapan.co.jp
| url = http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/detailview.html?KEY=SASCD-27
| accessdate = 2007-12-22
| archive-date = 2012-02-23
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120223134559/http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/detailview.html?KEY=SASCD-27
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>專輯於日本和歐洲同步發售，<ref name="lyrical">{{cite web
|url= http://www.jame-world.com/uk/news-24289-versailles-mini-album-japan-europe-release.html
|title= Versailles mini-album Japan & Europe Release
|accessdate= 2012-01-08
|author= Non-non
|date= 2007-09-01
|work= JaME World
|archive-date= 2019-02-15
|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190215160030/http://www.jame-world.com/uk/news-24289-versailles-mini-album-japan-europe-release.html
|dead-url= no
}}</ref>這種情況對於一支新組建的樂團來說是很不尋常的。這也是樂團與[[德國|德國]]唱片公司 {{tsl|en|CLJ Records|CLJ Records}} 簽約後發行的第一張作品。<ref name="jame">{{cite web |url=http://www.jame-world.com/cl/news-24367-lanzamiento-japones-y-europeo-de-versailles.html |title=Lanzamiento japonés y europeo de Versailles |accessdate=2017-03-27 |author=Non-Non, traducción de MaGeEc_TG |date=2007-09-03|publisher={{tsl|es|JaME|JaME}}. Japanese Music Entertainment |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801021143/http://www.jame-world.com/cl/news-24367-lanzamiento-japones-y-europeo-de-versailles.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>專輯的日本盤以 CD Only 形態發售，德國推出的歐洲盤則是CD+DVD，DVD收錄《Shout & Bites》的[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]。<ref name="jame2">{{cite web|url=http://www.jame-world.com/es/items-14377-lyrical-sympathy-limited-edition-.html|title=Lyrical Sympathy (Limited Edition)|accessdate=2017-03-27|publisher={{tsl|es|JaME|JaME}}. Japanese Music Entertainment|archive-date=2017-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170328015954/http://www.jame-world.com/es/items-14377-lyrical-sympathy-limited-edition-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="jame3">{{cite web |url=http://www.jame-world.com/es/items-14390-lyrical-sympathy.html |title=Lyrical Sympathy (Germany) |accessdate=2017-03-27 |publisher={{tsl|es|JaME|JaME}}. Japanese Music Entertainment |archive-date=2017-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170328020805/http://www.jame-world.com/es/items-14390-lyrical-sympathy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

來自此專輯的《The Red Carpet Day》和《Sympathia》兩首歌曲經過重新編曲，再次收錄於他們之後發行的五週年紀念版[[單曲|單曲]]《[[ROSE|ROSE]]》以及樂團的最後一張同名[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]《[[Versailles_(專輯)|Versailles]]》。

